Package com.lftechnology.java.training.alina.basic.packagejarexecute Description

This package consists of two functionalities, print number(NumberPrint Class) and add two numbers(NumberAdd Class).

  • NumberPrint Class :
    1. Create a Java application PrintNumber which prints number from 1-10.
    2. Create Executable Jar
    3. Run java application from command line.
    4. Print numbers
    5. Create JavaDoc of Application
  • NumberAdd Class :
    1. Create a Java application AddNumber, which takes two number from User and prints sum.
    2. Create Executable Jar
    3. Run java application from command line which should take values from user.
    4. Print sum
    5. Create JavaDoc of Application
